column_description: A unique identifier for each property
Foreign key referencing the address of the property in the 'Addresses' table
Foreign key referencing the user who owns the property in the 'Users' table
Foreign key referencing the type of property (e.g., flat, house) in the 'Ref_Property_Types' table
The date and time when the property was listed on the market
The date and time when the property was taken off the market
The name or title of the property (e.g., garden, studio)
A brief description of the property
Indicates whether the property has a garage (1 for yes, empty for no)
Indicates whether the property has parking lots (1 for yes, empty for no)
The number of rooms in the property
The price requested by the vendor for the property
The minimum acceptable price for the property
The maximum acceptable price for the property
Additional details about the property, if any
